This is the biggest moon, and - of course not in England,

00:00:52.075 --> 00:00:59.491
but in India - that day the moon is giving the greatest light,

00:01:00.199 --> 00:01:08.241
and it's such a great thing that Guru Nanaka was born on such a day.

00:01:09.200 --> 00:01:16.199
