00:02:50.658 --> 00:03:00.366
And he always took birth either in the most difficult places

00:03:00.408 --> 00:03:04.867
like hills and dales and mountains, or they took places --

00:03:06.034 --> 00:03:12.450
which are even more difficult thing, among the people who were horrid,

00:03:13.200 --> 00:03:16.200
and who needed their help.

00:03:16.867 --> 00:03:24.199
So in India, that time somehow Punjab was regarded as the place

00:03:24.200 --> 00:03:36.992
where people did not respect God or traditional Hindu idols,

00:03:37.658 --> 00:03:48.909
or you can say the statues that were regarded as the vibrating ones.

00:03:49.533 --> 00:03:55.200
