00:04:41.075 --> 00:04:45.742
between the followers of Mohammad and followers of Hinduism,

00:04:46.241 --> 00:04:50.533
Mohammad himself took his birth on this earth,

00:04:50.533 --> 00:04:55.950
though he had decided not to take any more births,

00:04:55.992 --> 00:04:58.200
he thought that it would solve the problem.

00:04:58.867 --> 00:05:02.533
