00:05:30.241 --> 00:05:32.117
to go to the incarnations.

00:05:32.742 --> 00:05:35.617
So, to celebrate his birthday

00:05:37.742 --> 00:05:44.325
on such a date is also a myth,

00:05:44.366 --> 00:05:48.199
because he never died. He is eternally living.

00:05:48.742 --> 00:05:53.325
