and is the most difficult thing for western people;

00:15:39.450 --> 00:15:41.533
because the matter is sitting on their Spirit.

00:15:43.658 --> 00:15:46.950
First the Spirit has to come - first phase --

00:15:47.533 --> 00:15:49.700
at least the Spirit has to be there.

00:15:50.909 --> 00:15:57.159
If you have to be the Spirit then thematter of moon

00:15:57.159 --> 00:15:59.575
has to be covered with that light.

