00:16:08.366 --> 00:16:12.034
First of all we must see that what are the things

00:16:12.450 --> 00:16:17.617
that drain out our bodily mastery.

00:16:18.199 --> 00:16:22.950
We must know all the crooks who try to master us.

00:16:23.366 --> 00:16:47.825
So I have to first face my body.

00:16:50.992 --> 00:16:55.742
That first and foremost thing in Sahaja Yoga we learn

00:16:56.241 --> 00:16:58.867
that we have to respect our body.

00:16:59.283 --> 00:17:04.034
This is the first principle of respecting our body.

00:17:04.533 --> 00:17:07.450
Means indulgence is sinful to the body,

00:17:07.909 --> 00:17:13.742
because indulgence gives you a body which is no good:

00:17:15.992 --> 00:17:18.742
First of all you must respect your body

00:17:18.783 --> 00:17:20.992
so that you can master it.

00:17:21.200 --> 00:17:23.325
If I do not respect you, I cannot master you.

00:17:23.742 --> 00:17:27.491
So to master the body first of all respect your body.

00:17:28.950 --> 00:17:33.491
