but if the temple is dirty,

00:18:52.658 --> 00:19:01.117
is sick, is unimpressive, is like a stick, or like a balloon,

00:19:01.450 --> 00:19:04.450
nobody is going to come near it.

00:19:06.533 --> 00:19:09.366
So try to improve your personality,

00:19:10.867 --> 00:19:13.825
that it has to be a beautiful temple.

