One should not go with the fashions of the day,

00:22:55.450 --> 00:22:58.283
and take to something which is nonsensical,

00:22:58.867 --> 00:23:02.909
which is not good for your appearance,

00:23:03.283 --> 00:23:07.199
which makes you look funny or very fashionable

00:23:07.200 --> 00:23:08.992
like a dandy person.

00:23:09.408 --> 00:23:14.783
We have to wear a dress which is in the centre, dignified, which is good.

00:23:20.783 --> 00:23:25.867
Now I'm told that it is very difficult even to wake up in England.

00:23:26.533 --> 00:23:28.950
Somebody had told me, when I was young,

00:23:29.325 --> 00:23:31.658
that don't wake up an Englishman.

00:23:33.742 --> 00:23:37.491
I haven't tried that, even with a barge pole.

00:23:38.241 --> 00:23:41.742
I just tell you at this time, never in the morning time.

00:23:42.159 --> 00:23:44.992
Because I've been warned: never wake up an Englishman,

00:23:44.992 --> 00:23:47.283
that is the greatest sin on this earth!

00:23:53.825 --> 00:23:57.533
So why should the English be so much addicted to sleep!

00:23:58.200 --> 00:24:01.075
The whole country is sleeping today.

00:24:01.617 --> 00:24:05.491
They want more wages, more wages so that they can sleep more.

00:24:07.325 --> 00:24:11.241
Eat and drink, drink and eat in between, sleep.

00:24:11.283 --> 00:24:16.658
This is the three - programmed life.

00:24:19.533 --> 00:24:23.283
It was very difficult, from the very beginnig

00:24:23.325 --> 00:24:28.491
I saw Sahaja Yogis coming, in that to wake them up was difficult.

00:24:28.533 --> 00:24:34.283
And these are the same people who were known for punctuality

00:24:34.325 --> 00:24:38.992
that they won the war at Waterloo because of punctuality,

00:24:39.742 --> 00:24:45.159
and they were so punctual that people used to set their watches --

00:24:45.199 --> 00:24:47.992
even in America. They are the same people.

00:24:48.533 --> 00:24:52.992
Now the other side of it is that they sleep like log of wood.

00:24:53.450 --> 00:24:56.159
They used to sleep before also must be, because this is an old saying that.

00:24:56.199 --> 00:24:57.950
Don't wake up an Englishman.

00:24:58.742 --> 00:25:02.992
But I used to think something else about it why it is said,

00:25:02.992 --> 00:25:05.742
but it is nothing but simple laziness.

00:25:07.200 --> 00:25:14.117
So try to see why we sleep so much.

00:25:18.034 --> 00:25:22.159
If the left side is strong, people sleep.

00:25:23.075 --> 00:25:27.366
If the back Agnya is strong, people sleep.

00:25:27.533 --> 00:25:33.867
If the front Agnya is working too much

00:25:34.408 --> 00:25:36.783
then people don't sleep.

00:25:39.408 --> 00:25:42.408
So even if I say, "Don't sleep",

00:25:42.742 --> 00:25:48.034
it mean that you put your right Agnya in working condition,

00:25:48.034 --> 00:25:50.034
that means you start thinking.

00:25:50.075 --> 00:25:51.825
Which is against Sahaja Yoga again.

00:25:53.075 --> 00:25:56.034
So it would be left agnya, right agnya, right agnya, left agnya,

00:25:56.034 --> 00:25:57.325
left agnya, left agnya, right agnya, left agnya...

00:25:57.325 --> 00:25:59.575
It will be going from one to another.

00:26:01.658 --> 00:26:10.533
So in the centre you have to be with Christ.

00:26:14.199 --> 00:26:19.199
He is alert every second of the day;

00:26:24.992 --> 00:26:28.283
killing; beating, hitting,

00:26:29.533 --> 00:26:35.867
curing, looking after, guiding.

00:26:36.658 --> 00:26:45.742
Twenty four hours a day. And go and ask any realized soul

00:26:45.783 --> 00:26:48.450
who is called as Avadhuta, the one who is a master,

00:26:48.491 --> 00:26:52.783
they will tell you they hardly sleep for three hours or four hours.

00:26:53.450 --> 00:26:56.950
Because they cannot work when they are sleeping,

00:26:57.199 --> 00:26:58.700
so they sleep for four hours,

00:26:58.742 --> 00:27:00.617
the rest of the time they are working:

00:27:01.325 --> 00:27:05.617
either they meditate and do things by projection,

00:27:06.159 --> 00:27:09.450
or they work with their hands.

00:27:10.034 --> 00:27:12.783
They are busy people, they are very busy.

00:27:13.283 --> 00:27:20.700
You have to be very busy people because now you are employed by God.

00:27:21.199 --> 00:27:26.575
And you have to do full justice to this employment by working hard.

00:27:27.199 --> 00:27:33.450
On the contrary you have seen that it is very easy to get lazy.

00:27:39.241 --> 00:27:44.034
So now, as many of you are already feeling sleepy, put your....

00:27:44.867 --> 00:27:48.199
First thing should be for all those people who are lazy,

00:27:48.199 --> 00:27:50.992
is to put their right to the left seven times -

00:27:51.075 --> 00:27:52.366
let's have it.

00:27:55.159 --> 00:27:57.575
With the right hand....

00:28:12.992 --> 00:28:18.199
It's better? Now the back Agnya.

00:28:18.199 --> 00:28:20.075
Let's have it.

00:28:22.992 --> 00:28:29.950
Laziness is first. Shri Krishna was against laziness.

00:28:29.950 --> 00:28:35.034
Anywhere he got a chance he talked against laziness, Alasya.

00:28:36.992 --> 00:28:38.909
Now watch me.

00:28:39.825 --> 00:28:41.950
On the photograph you can do the same....

00:29:39.950 --> 00:29:41.617
Better now?

00:29:45.491 --> 00:29:49.199
Tonight we have to keep awake; it's a big problem.

00:29:50.909 --> 00:29:53.825
But don't sleep formally here. Alright ?

00:29:53.950 --> 00:29:55.867
Informally you can.

00:30:09.950 --> 00:30:11.867
Better ?

00:30:14.075 --> 00:30:17.658
Put your eyes, try Again.

00:30:49.909 --> 00:30:54.034
So the mastery should be, first of all, of your body.

00:30:55.867 --> 00:30:58.742
Say, you are sleeping on one side, you get a pain --

00:30:58.742 --> 00:31:00.950
then what do you do? You sleep on the other side.

00:31:02.742 --> 00:31:06.825
In the same way, this body is to be made

00:31:06.825 --> 00:31:10.533
immune to different shocks,

00:31:10.575 --> 00:31:13.867
you see. Like you put the watch in the water.

00:31:14.325 --> 00:31:17.658
You shock it with the water, so it is waterproof.

00:31:18.117 --> 00:31:21.366
So a Sahaja Yogi has to be an all-proofed person.

00:31:23.034 --> 00:31:31.950
So he has no place to complain,

00:31:32.658 --> 00:31:35.075
because he's supposed to be all-proof, you see.

00:31:35.117 --> 00:31:38.159
Anybody (Sahaja Yogi) who complains, you can say,

00:31:38.199 --> 00:31:39.992
"How are you complaining?

00:31:39.992 --> 00:31:41.575
Because you have to be all-proof."

00:31:43.366 --> 00:31:53.159
So no complaints of any kind, of Sahaja Yogis

00:31:53.199 --> 00:31:55.575
are to be accepted or sympathized.

00:32:01.241 --> 00:32:06.491
If you start accepting people who are complaining type

00:32:07.075 --> 00:32:09.408
you will be always busy looking after them,

00:32:09.909 --> 00:32:13.450
and you will be of no use to Sahaja Yoga.

00:32:15.199 --> 00:32:18.992
Those who have habits of complaininig and all that

00:32:19.034 --> 00:32:21.117
should go to the hospital and stay there.

00:32:21.742 --> 00:32:25.408
Complaining people are really people

00:32:25.450 --> 00:32:28.283
who have some sort of possession,

00:32:28.325 --> 00:32:32.366
I think, that they all the time complain and try to torture you,

00:32:32.909 --> 00:32:35.199
and make a nuisance out of themselves.

00:32:35.909 --> 00:32:38.199
Such people cannot become Gurus.

00:32:38.199 --> 00:32:43.034
Imagine - if the Guru is complaining then what is he going to teach?

00:32:43.075 --> 00:32:44.867
Only complaining.

00:32:45.617 --> 00:32:48.700
The teachers will be expert in complaining

00:32:48.700 --> 00:32:50.950
and the students will be also experts in complaining.

00:32:51.283 --> 00:32:56.117
So you create a set of complaining disciples, you see,

00:32:57.408 --> 00:32:59.533
And when they come to Me what I find

00:32:59.575 --> 00:33:03.325
they all have double lists than yourselves about their complaints.

00:33:05.200 --> 00:33:07.617
But also it is very characteristic.

00:33:07.658 --> 00:33:09.867
Like Australians seldom complain,

00:33:10.491 --> 00:33:13.159
and if they do complain they are hit also very badly.

00:33:13.700 --> 00:33:16.783
Seldom you will find an Australian complaining.

00:33:16.783 --> 00:33:18.950
I have got letters - except one or two

00:33:19.366 --> 00:33:22.283
who have now found themselves out - seldom

00:33:22.950 --> 00:33:27.283
they complain about themselves, about their body comforts,

00:33:27.283 --> 00:33:30.450
this thing that thing. So under any circumstances

00:33:30.992 --> 00:33:35.783
those who can live are the people

00:33:36.200 --> 00:33:38.742
who have achieved the one sixteenth,

00:33:39.199 --> 00:33:40.783
only the one sixteenth.

00:33:41.034 --> 00:33:43.742
(Jaise rakhahu taise hi rahu)

00:33:43.742 --> 00:33:47.450
Mother the way you keep it we are willing to stay.

00:33:47.992 --> 00:33:50.992
Of course the Mother has kept you very well.

00:33:54.491 --> 00:33:57.241
All the luxuries of world Mother has given you.

00:33:58.825 --> 00:34:01.575
She doesn't torture you like other Gurus have tortured.

00:34:02.075 --> 00:34:03.825
Once and for all.

00:34:04.199 --> 00:34:07.034
My Son has gone through all the tortures,

00:34:08.241 --> 00:34:13.200
there is no need to put you to any tortures or troubles.

00:34:13.408 --> 00:34:15.658
But you should see how your body reacts,

00:34:15.700 --> 00:34:20.700
and tell your body, "Yes Mr body, will you please now,

00:34:20.700 --> 00:34:23.825
behave yourself and not try to be indulgent."

00:34:25.700 --> 00:34:32.117
All these indulgences come to us through our senses.

00:34:32.617 --> 00:34:35.909
So if you can master your body

00:34:35.909 --> 00:34:38.408
you will also master your senses.

00:34:38.950 --> 00:34:49.658
For example the master, or we say the highest of the organs

00:34:49.700 --> 00:34:53.241
which controls most of the organs, I personally think, is the tongue.

00:34:53.909 --> 00:34:58.408
Because it's the primordial nonsense.

00:35:01.658 --> 00:35:08.034
By tongue we speak things to hurt others.

00:35:08.658 --> 00:35:13.408
With tongue we learn how to go on jabbering.

00:35:13.992 --> 00:35:17.867
With tongue we can show how frivolous we are.

00:35:18.575 --> 00:35:21.783
Either we are tongue tied or tongue - loose,

00:35:22.075 --> 00:35:24.700
there's nothing in between with the tongue.

00:35:24.700 --> 00:35:27.117
That's only about talking part, that's lower.

00:35:27.533 --> 00:35:31.159
But when it comes higher, eating;

00:35:33.159 --> 00:35:35.199
all the time thinking about eating.

00:35:35.199 --> 00:35:38.783
I have told you a hundred times, that Sahaja Yogis should go

00:35:38.783 --> 00:35:44.283
on really sometimes on absolutely bland boiled horrible food --

00:35:45.700 --> 00:35:52.700
just to test the tongue. Do it, try this, then try this.

00:35:52.950 --> 00:35:56.867
My father used to tell that you must burn your tongue a little bit.

00:35:57.366 --> 00:35:59.909
That's one of the tests he said one should do.

00:35:59.909 --> 00:36:02.117
But he was a hard taskmaster as a Guru.

00:36:02.700 --> 00:36:05.783
So we should see what our tongue can bear,

00:36:06.366 --> 00:36:09.199
is it fussy about food ?

00:36:14.117 --> 00:36:19.283
When it sees the food does it start watering, first of all;

00:36:23.575 --> 00:36:26.491
does it take our attention to food,

00:36:27.075 --> 00:36:28.992
is food important to us?

00:36:29.491 --> 00:36:42.034
So the first thing, to overcome the problem of your tongue is

00:36:42.034 --> 00:36:46.783
"to starve." Starvation is the only way

00:36:46.825 --> 00:36:50.325
you can correct yourself. You see if you starve yourself --

00:36:50.408 --> 00:36:56.909
say, morning just have little to eat, reduce it to half.

00:36:56.950 --> 00:36:59.783
You'll be surprised your intestine will be halved also.

00:36:59.783 --> 00:37:02.700
After some time you cannot eat more even if you want to.

00:37:03.408 --> 00:37:07.700
Your interest will go off. Train up yourself.

00:37:07.742 --> 00:37:09.742
Starvation is a very good thing.

00:37:09.742 --> 00:37:13.241
I think 40 days that Christ did is a very good idea.

00:37:15.783 --> 00:37:20.783
But that should not be a kind of a thing that like - they have Ramazan,

00:37:21.159 --> 00:37:26.867
that they eat the most s..... food during that time early in the morning

00:37:26.867 --> 00:37:29.283
then the whole day they starve - thinking about food!

00:37:32.491 --> 00:37:38.575
Starve yourself fully and don't think about food.

00:37:38.575 --> 00:37:40.825
That's difficult so starve yourself  in halfway

00:37:41.199 --> 00:37:42.700
and dont think about food.

00:37:44.159 --> 00:37:46.909
Gradually try to master your tongue.

00:37:47.658 --> 00:37:51.241
Mastery of your tongue is only possible if you know

00:37:51.283 --> 00:37:54.450
how to starve your day. This is for the western side.

00:37:54.533 --> 00:37:58.491
For eastern side they fast morning till evening.

00:37:59.742 --> 00:38:02.117
I know one lady, if you ask them they say

00:38:02.159 --> 00:38:06.200
"I observe Monday, I observe Tuesday, I observe Wednesday,

00:38:06.241 --> 00:38:09.825
I observe Thursday, I observe Friday a fast,

00:38:09.867 --> 00:38:16.075
and perhaps maybe if I do not starve Saturday I will eat on Sunday."

00:38:16.909 --> 00:38:20.200
I have know such people in my life time - many --

00:38:20.742 --> 00:38:22.909
who just go on fasting.

00:38:22.909 --> 00:38:25.034
They are such experts and astute? you see,

00:38:25.658 --> 00:38:29.575
that they can show you that they can fast for 50 days, 80 days,

00:38:29.575 --> 00:38:33.617
108 days, and 300 days.

00:38:34.117 --> 00:38:36.200
Starving masters.

00:38:36.700 --> 00:38:40.450
So for them I have to tell, "you have to eat'', when they are starve.

00:38:40.491 --> 00:38:42.075
To you I have to say,

00:38:42.075 --> 00:38:45.742
"Let us see which day we can starve ourselves."

00:38:45.742 --> 00:38:52.199
Let us have one day to celebrate today's great day of Nanaka!

00:38:52.199 --> 00:38:55.867
One day let us starve. Which day should we?

00:38:58.117 --> 00:39:02.950
Monday we cannot because Monday we have a programme,

00:39:04.533 --> 00:39:10.117
Tuesday we cannot because it is a day when Hanuman has to work,

00:39:13.783 --> 00:39:16.825
Wednesday we cannot, because then the creativity takes place,

00:39:18.408 --> 00:39:21.700
Thursday we cannot because we are Guru at that day,

00:39:21.742 --> 00:39:24.950
we have to work very hard as Gurus, Friday we cannot,

00:39:24.992 --> 00:39:27.117
we have to work the shakti of Mother,

00:39:27.117 --> 00:39:29.617
Saturday we cannot because we have to do

00:39:29.617 --> 00:39:33.491
all the intrigue of Shri Krishna.

00:39:34.199 --> 00:39:37.408
And Sunday how can it be, this is the day of the sun!"

00:39:40.117 --> 00:39:44.199
So which is the best day for starving, now let us see.

00:39:45.366 --> 00:39:51.658
We should have Thursday, because Thursday is the Guru's day

00:39:51.992 --> 00:39:56.658
and let us do some fasting, half day, half day can we?

00:39:56.700 --> 00:39:59.909
Can we start with half day then f... day?

00:39:59.909 --> 00:40:02.909
Thursday let us have, maybe second half

00:40:02.909 --> 00:40:05.283
because breakfast is essential I think.

00:40:06.366 --> 00:40:09.617
Without breakfast you see, the horses cannot whinny,

00:40:12.283 --> 00:40:14.366
so let us have the second half

00:40:17.742 --> 00:40:20.117
or we can have the first half.

00:40:20.867 --> 00:40:26.491
Actually you have to discipline yourself, if you have to be the Gurus.

00:40:26.533 --> 00:40:29.283
It's like going to a college,

00:40:29.491 --> 00:40:31.325
when you are left to yourself,

00:40:31.366 --> 00:40:34.241
it is you, who has to discipline yourself,

00:40:34.283 --> 00:40:37.199
nobody has to tell you that you do this and do that

00:40:37.199 --> 00:40:39.408
That's the measure to wake you up.

00:40:39.450 --> 00:40:42.491
In India it is the other way around.

00:40:42.491 --> 00:40:45.825
If you tell somebody that you have to wake up at 5,

00:40:46.617 --> 00:40:51.867
the person who has told you will be awakened at 4 o' clock himself,

00:40:51.909 --> 00:40:56.200
the one who has told; so that he doesn't get up to wake him up.

00:40:56.950 --> 00:40:58.700
Did you follow me?

00:40:59.241 --> 00:41:01.950
And the whole house will be awakened at 4 o'clock

00:41:02.366 --> 00:41:05.325
so that they can take up the duty from the person

00:41:05.325 --> 00:41:06.825
who has to get awakened.

00:41:09.159 --> 00:41:10.950
But the fellow who has to awaken

00:41:10.992 --> 00:41:12.658
might not sleep the whole night.

00:41:13.617 --> 00:41:17.075
It is just the other way round, the other extreme of it.

00:41:17.491 --> 00:41:23.825
Say if I am there, one night I sleep there. If I get up

00:41:24.366 --> 00:41:27.575
at one o'clock I find all of them sitting and meditating,

00:41:27.575 --> 00:41:30.199
in the passage, up to the bathroom everywhere.

00:41:30.200 --> 00:41:33.241
They have not gone home, not taken food, nothing.

00:41:33.742 --> 00:41:36.283
Just meditating, taking vibrations, correcting.

00:41:36.283 --> 00:41:37.950
I am sleeping inside.

00:41:37.950 --> 00:41:40.199
In the night I want to go to the bathroom,

00:41:40.199 --> 00:41:42.325
I just cannot go because they are all meditating.

00:41:42.366 --> 00:41:44.533
Nobody is sleeping, nobody is sleeping.

00:41:50.950 --> 00:41:53.241
So it is the other way around.

00:41:54.199 --> 00:41:56.867
So to you people let us do one day.

00:41:56.867 --> 00:42:02.199
That you must have one day fasting, one day keeping, one awake.

00:42:02.742 --> 00:42:05.283
Which day should it be? Let's see.

00:42:08.283 --> 00:42:10.867
A day when there is no film!

00:42:18.658 --> 00:42:25.909
Half night, second half I mean, not the first half.

00:42:29.783 --> 00:42:41.200
Which day? Which is the most difficult day when you cannot,

00:42:43.199 --> 00:42:51.034
cannot keep awake. Sunday night;

00:42:52.034 --> 00:42:54.658
but there's a fiIm on!

00:42:57.366 --> 00:43:00.700
Without the film, you see!

00:43:00.700 --> 00:43:03.783
Treat yourself like that, joke with yourself,

00:43:03.783 --> 00:43:06.617
now Sunday night is there a film on?

00:43:06.658 --> 00:43:08.283
After 12 there isn't.

00:43:08.325 --> 00:43:10.658
So Sunday night you get up at 12 o'clock.

00:43:10.700 --> 00:43:17.992
Let's have it. Enjoy it. Don't get angry.

00:43:20.034 --> 00:43:22.159
Make a fun out of it.

00:43:25.034 --> 00:43:29.199
You think more about it, then you get upset.

00:43:29.200 --> 00:43:31.241
You just don't think about it, then you'll enjoy it.

00:43:31.241 --> 00:43:32.783
It's like swimming.

00:43:32.825 --> 00:43:37.325
Get up at 12 o'clock, all of you, go for a bath, sit down,

00:43:37.366 --> 00:43:41.034
sing Bhajans, this, that, let us do it. Should we ?

00:43:45.783 --> 00:43:48.742
Michel, What happen with you?

00:43:48.783 --> 00:43:55.241
"I can go to bed at two o clock"

00:43:55.241 --> 00:43:59.159
You have to get up at 12 o'clock,

00:43:59.159 --> 00:44:03.200
you have to go to bed till 12 o'clock.

00:44:03.241 --> 00:44:05.200
Get up at 12 o'clock.

00:44:05.241 --> 00:44:09.199
You see the first half of the night, one must sleep always, it's better.

00:44:09.408 --> 00:44:13.700
Second half of the night is the better part, alright?

00:44:13.909 --> 00:44:17.075
So the first half of the night you all have to sleep, anytime.

00:44:17.117 --> 00:44:20.200
You can sleep about 8 o'clock or 9 o'clock if you want to.

00:44:22.742 --> 00:44:25.950
But that should not be important, what time you sleep,

00:44:25.950 --> 00:44:29.075
you have to get up at 12 o'clock in the morning,

00:44:29.742 --> 00:44:31.909
or say after 12.

00:44:35.783 --> 00:44:38.867
Shri Krishna was born in the night about 12 o'clock.

00:44:38.867 --> 00:44:41.075
Nanaka was born 12 o'clock in the night.

00:44:41.075 --> 00:44:45.283
All the Gurus mostly took their birth at 12 o'clock in the night.

00:44:46.117 --> 00:44:51.742
To celebrate that, we must have one day when we do not sleep after 12.

00:44:52.408 --> 00:44:56.199
But then what about Caxton Hall!

00:44:56.658 --> 00:44:59.742
"Mother we can try this on Saturday.

00:44:59.825 --> 00:45:01.325
多What?

00:45:01.825 --> 00:45:04.450
多Can we do it in Saturday night? It will be more safe

00:45:04.783 --> 00:45:07.450
because will be less incidents the Sunday that Monday"

00:45:07.617 --> 00:45:15.117
Alright so you can sleep in the day time of Saturday or of Sunday.

