They will never, take it from me, they will not:

00:45:54.742 --> 00:45:57.199
You see work is not important what is important

00:45:57.200 --> 00:46:02.700
is your Spirit, your mastery.

00:46:02.742 --> 00:46:06.241
Work, in any case you're not going to have after some time,

00:46:06.992 --> 00:46:09.241
so that work is not important.

00:46:09.283 --> 00:46:12.533
This new work that you have taken, better look after that.

00:46:12.533 --> 00:46:16.533
Forget about your work. Forget about these things.

00:46:16.575 --> 00:46:19.159
What is important is your Spirit.

00:46:19.199 --> 00:46:21.408
Otherwise you cannot become Gurus.

00:46:22.199 --> 00:46:24.199
Spirit is the most important thing.

00:46:24.200 --> 00:46:27.867
The rest of the things are absolutely unimportant,

00:46:27.867 --> 00:46:29.783
a zero.

00:46:32.617 --> 00:46:37.408
I've been very slowly trying to take you out

00:46:37.450 --> 00:46:41.867
of the mud of materialism and of these mundane things.

00:46:42.366 --> 00:46:47.491
But you have to work for God. You are special people.

00:46:49.034 --> 00:46:53.450
So, you have to make yourself a master,

00:46:55.159 --> 00:47:00.491
so God gives you all the blessings, everything.

00:47:01.491 --> 00:47:04.909
But the idea of luxurious life must be given up.

00:47:05.617 --> 00:47:09.117
People want to make this life luxurious,

00:47:09.992 --> 00:47:12.408
then you'll have the luxury of this world

00:47:12.450 --> 00:47:15.533
but not the luxury of God's blessings.

00:47:16.075 --> 00:47:18.159
One of the two you have to select.

00:47:18.617 --> 00:47:31.909
Either you lead a life which is luxurious on the material level,

00:47:32.034 --> 00:47:35.909
or you lead a luxurious life of God's blessings.

00:47:35.909 --> 00:47:38.783
One of the two you have to choose, the time has come.

00:47:39.241 --> 00:47:42.742
So nothing is important you see,

00:47:42.742 --> 00:47:46.117
the insecurity of money also is another nonsense.

00:47:46.117 --> 00:47:48.325
At least you people should not have it.

00:47:49.117 --> 00:47:51.742
I mean you will never starve at least,

00:47:51.783 --> 00:47:55.117
but Indians if they do not work they will starve.

00:47:57.450 --> 00:48:00.617
But you people can never starve, if you are unemployed,

00:48:00.617 --> 00:48:06.075
government is happy more, as long as you don't bother them.

00:48:06.950 --> 00:48:09.658
If you sit at home and meditate

00:48:09.700 --> 00:48:11.117
they'll be very happy.

00:48:12.159 --> 00:48:17.617
So to earn more money or to make more money

00:48:17.658 --> 00:48:19.825
is not important at all in Sahaja Yoga.

00:48:21.658 --> 00:48:24.742
Most important thing is to be the Spirit.

00:48:24.783 --> 00:48:26.992
For that whatever is to be done has to be done.

00:48:27.700 --> 00:48:33.491
Let everything suffer, you don't make your Spirit suffer.

00:48:36.075 --> 00:48:44.617
Because you have to become the full moon, like Guru Nanak.

00:48:45.283 --> 00:48:48.491
How much did Guru Nanak earn?

00:48:53.742 --> 00:49:01.034
You should find out, how did he live his life ?

00:49:06.825 --> 00:49:12.034
There is nothing to bother about money,

00:49:12.992 --> 00:49:16.075
because more money is not needed.

00:49:18.700 --> 00:49:23.199
Just needed for your food and your living.

00:49:24.700 --> 00:49:27.658
And then money is arranged if you need

00:49:27.658 --> 00:49:29.700
any extra money sometimes, emergencies.

00:49:29.742 --> 00:49:32.283
I've done it for many Australians, you know.

00:49:32.700 --> 00:49:36.742
But those are the people who have dedicated themselves fully.

00:49:38.909 --> 00:49:41.283
And that is why they have been helped,

00:49:41.325 --> 00:49:43.783
whenever there is an emergency they don't have to bother.

00:49:44.366 --> 00:49:49.241
But the dedication to your Spirit has to be full, complete,

00:49:49.867 --> 00:49:53.366
and nothing to your work, actually.

00:49:54.117 --> 00:49:56.783
Because that goes hand in hand.

00:49:57.617 --> 00:50:02.034
If you are not worried about yourself after realisation,

00:50:03.199 --> 00:50:07.283
about your Spirit, you'll have all the problems of the world.

00:50:07.867 --> 00:50:10.117
First and foremost is financial problems.

00:50:16.199 --> 00:50:25.199
Then, physical problem, mental problem, emotional problem.

00:50:25.867 --> 00:50:27.867
All kinds of problems will follow,

00:50:27.909 --> 00:50:31.909
because I've awakened your Kundalini; one part I've done.

00:50:32.867 --> 00:50:35.533
But another part that is your heart, you have not opened.

00:50:35.575 --> 00:50:37.867
You must give your heart to Sahaja Yoga.

00:50:38.408 --> 00:50:40.491
You have not opened your heart as yet.

00:50:41.200 --> 00:50:44.117
Heart has to be opened.

00:50:44.617 --> 00:50:47.075
You are still woried about your father, mother,

00:50:47.117 --> 00:50:48.950
brother, sister, wife, children.

00:50:49.658 --> 00:50:56.034
Open your heart fully to Sahaja Yoga.

00:50:56.617 --> 00:50:58.658
In a doubtless way.

00:50:59.200 --> 00:51:01.658
Then only doubt less awareness will settle down.

00:51:02.283 --> 00:51:05.034
Unless and until you open your heart,

00:51:05.200 --> 00:51:07.325
Kundalini rising has no meaning.

00:51:07.909 --> 00:51:12.408
Because the Kundalini is rising but the heart has not opened.

00:51:13.034 --> 00:51:17.117
If the Mother Earth sends forth her power through the seed

00:51:17.117 --> 00:51:20.199
and the seed doesn't open, then what's the use ?

00:51:20.199 --> 00:51:21.950
It's all a myth.

00:51:21.992 --> 00:51:24.199
Open your heart to Sahaja Yoga.

00:51:24.408 --> 00:51:27.117
Open your heart to Spirit, and say,

00:51:27.117 --> 00:51:29.075
"Mother we are the Spirit."

00:51:31.117 --> 00:51:32.700
You have to realize this,

00:51:32.742 --> 00:51:34.783
many people also perhaps do no realize

00:51:34.783 --> 00:51:38.575
that you have come on this earth to be the Spirit

00:51:39.034 --> 00:51:41.867
and not to be workers of human beings.

00:51:43.617 --> 00:51:49.408
You must understand your greatness and know

00:51:49.450 --> 00:51:53.450
that you are not like mundan people. That's why you are blessed.

00:51:54.075 --> 00:51:55.742
Who is blessed so much ?

00:51:56.325 --> 00:51:59.117
You are described long time back by Blake,

00:51:59.617 --> 00:52:02.408
that such and such people are going to come on this earth

00:52:02.450 --> 00:52:04.825
"men of God." Men of God.

00:52:06.366 --> 00:52:09.742
What do you have in your heart?

00:52:11.617 --> 00:52:14.992
Your heart will be like a stone.

00:52:15.491 --> 00:52:18.450
Unless and until there is light of the Spirit

00:52:18.450 --> 00:52:20.867
it is a stone heart,

00:52:20.909 --> 00:52:28.825
and this stone is going to hurt everyone, is going to ruin you completely.

00:52:29.283 --> 00:52:33.366
Open your heart hundred percent.

00:52:38.575 --> 00:52:41.034
You have met Indian Sahaja Yogis,

00:52:42.159 --> 00:52:43.742
they have problems of money.

00:52:44.742 --> 00:52:47.700
And how much they work for Sahaja Yoga,

00:52:48.159 --> 00:52:53.825
day in and day out how much they have contributed for Sahaja Yoga.

00:52:54.366 --> 00:52:59.199
You can imagine, about 7 lakhs of rupees they have collected,

00:52:59.199 --> 00:53:06.658
Rustom knows. 7 lakhs of rupees, they have collected for their ashram.

00:53:07.200 --> 00:53:16.325
7 lakhs is about 贈35000.贈 35000 they have collected only in Bombay.

00:53:16.617 --> 00:53:20.992
In Delhi they have collected about 5 lakhs, 贈 25000.

00:53:23.909 --> 00:53:26.742
They are working, they have families they have children,

00:53:27.283 --> 00:53:30.867
but what they think about is nothing but Sahaja Yoga,

00:53:30.867 --> 00:53:32.909
nothing but Sahaja Yoga, nothing but Sahaja Yoga.

00:53:39.159 --> 00:53:42.783
They give most of their money for Sahaja Yoga, I think.

00:53:43.617 --> 00:53:45.366
They live with minimum.

00:53:45.909 --> 00:53:50.117
If I tell them why don't you buy another shirt for yourself,

00:53:50.783 --> 00:53:56.575
they will say, "Mother, I have worn lots of shirts in my previous life,"

00:53:59.199 --> 00:54:02.950
So satisfied ! "We have found the Atma now,

00:54:02.992 --> 00:54:05.325
let us dress up the Atma.

00:54:05.366 --> 00:54:09.491
We have found out our heart, let us become the heart".

00:54:09.533 --> 00:54:11.950
What is the need to worry about these things ?

00:54:11.992 --> 00:54:14.241
We have done enough of all this nonsense.

00:54:15.034 --> 00:54:19.491
I tell you they will think they are poor, but they are not.

00:54:20.909 --> 00:54:23.783
Wherever they can save their money they will save it.

00:54:24.283 --> 00:54:26.783
They used to give me some money before, I said,

00:54:26.825 --> 00:54:28.950
"No I don't need just now, there's no need"

00:54:28.950 --> 00:54:30.867
They said I have no place to keep;

00:54:30.909 --> 00:54:33.034
there is no trust, nothing, how are we to do it?

00:54:33.575 --> 00:54:43.533
They continued like this till about, I think, in, 74,

00:54:47.825 --> 00:54:51.283
when I went back we thought of starting an ashram,

00:54:51.325 --> 00:54:53.867
because you people were all coming there.

00:54:55.909 --> 00:55:01.617
So I said alright, now you have to give me money,

00:55:01.658 --> 00:55:04.783
all the Sahaja Yogis can give me money, whatever they have saved.

00:55:05.283 --> 00:55:08.325
And you'll be amazed everyone came out with 1000 rupees,

00:55:08.366 --> 00:55:13.533
every one of them, whether he was a labourer or every one of them,

00:55:13.575 --> 00:55:18.075
1000 rupees minimum. Up to 21 000.

00:55:18.825 --> 00:55:22.034
In 3 years time they had saved,

00:55:22.075 --> 00:55:23.950
because they thought it is our responsibility

00:55:23.992 --> 00:55:25.575
to save money for Sahaja Yoga.

00:55:25.617 --> 00:55:27.992
Tomorrow if we have to have an ashram how are we going to have ?

00:55:33.199 --> 00:55:35.950
But we still indulge into things.

00:55:43.742 --> 00:55:48.075
So this is what is the Gurupada.

00:55:48.117 --> 00:55:53.992
This Sir has to sit down, make an space for him.

00:55:54.034 --> 00:55:57.575
Come on, please. He doesn't need to be stand up. All right.

00:56:01.700 --> 00:56:05.366
So today is such a great day of Guru Nanaka's birthday,

00:56:06.325 --> 00:56:10.491
and we have to see his own life, how he spent his own life,

00:56:10.825 --> 00:56:16.992
how he lived and in what conditions he managed.

00:56:19.199 --> 00:56:24.034
So the first thing is to look after, disciplining yourself,

00:56:24.617 --> 00:56:28.283
feeling responsible for Sahaja Yoga.

00:56:29.117 --> 00:56:33.075
I was amazed people told, me that in the ashram

00:56:33.117 --> 00:56:38.199
people keep the lights on, and the oil costs so much,

00:56:38.200 --> 00:56:43.159
300 pounds every week. I'm amazed!

00:56:44.450 --> 00:56:48.700
Every one of you should be responsi-be for every electricity,

00:56:48.700 --> 00:56:52.408
everything that you spend here. This is God's place.

00:56:56.159 --> 00:57:00.325
Somebody has given the car, everybody wants to use the car.

00:57:00.366 --> 00:57:02.658
You see this saving the pounds

00:57:02.700 --> 00:57:05.117
is still going on the heads of Sahaja Yogis.

00:57:05.950 --> 00:57:09.117
If they can save by taking somebody's car they would borrow.

00:57:09.159 --> 00:57:10.575
Never borrow anybody's car.

00:57:10.575 --> 00:57:12.950
It's not for you, you must have your self respect,

00:57:12.950 --> 00:57:14.617
why to borrow anybody's car?

00:57:14.617 --> 00:57:16.992
It's not to be done.

00:57:20.199 --> 00:57:24.034
So the second point of the Self is self respect.

00:57:24.617 --> 00:57:27.783
First is the respect of your body,

00:57:28.325 --> 00:57:30.867
and the second is self-respect.

00:57:34.617 --> 00:57:38.825
We are arrogant, we can be rude,

00:57:40.658 --> 00:57:42.491
but we have no self respect.

00:57:51.617 --> 00:57:54.783
But it is the training that is lacking,

00:57:55.450 --> 00:57:57.783
you see suddenly I find after war

00:57:57.783 --> 00:58:03.992
there has been no teaching how to be self respecting.

00:58:06.199 --> 00:58:11.408
Like in the war, might be, the atmosphere might have been created I don't know why - that-

00:58:11.408 --> 00:58:14.117
"I卒m above everything, don't care for others."

00:58:17.034 --> 00:58:20.199
May have been; I don't know why this kind of a thing has come,

00:58:20.199 --> 00:58:22.325
but it is so. Very prevalent.

00:58:22.366 --> 00:58:24.783
But you people have to be other way round:

00:58:25.283 --> 00:58:28.700
'Others are first and then yourself.

00:58:28.700 --> 00:58:30.325
With your self respect.

00:58:30.325 --> 00:58:33.658
Doesn't matter, nobody is going to die, I can tell you this much.

00:58:40.408 --> 00:58:45.366
You all must have self respect; and such mediocre people

00:58:45.825 --> 00:58:48.491
should not be allowed to stay in Sahaja Yoga,

00:58:51.199 --> 00:58:56.325
at least in the ashram, because it brings a bad name to all Sahaja Yoga.

00:58:56.325 --> 00:58:58.450
One person can spoil the whole.

00:58:58.950 --> 00:59:03.283
Only people who want to be Gurus have to stay in the ashram.

00:59:03.325 --> 00:59:06.117
It's not going to be made a convenience for anyone.

00:59:08.283 --> 00:59:12.199
But the other way around is that,

00:59:12.200 --> 00:59:14.825
"We are going to look after ourselves,

00:59:14.867 --> 00:59:17.950
we have to become this, we have to grow,

00:59:17.992 --> 00:59:19.658
we have to do it."

00:59:25.199 --> 00:59:29.159
Then it's just, the other way round, everything works out,

00:59:29.199 --> 00:59:31.034
I don't have to tell you.

00:59:31.075 --> 00:59:33.408
You know this is so base and so gross

00:59:33.867 --> 00:59:35.783
that after being here for so many years,

00:59:36.533 --> 00:59:41.199
you should all have become avadhutas by now, absolutely.

00:59:41.199 --> 00:59:43.700
Controlling all elements, everything, should have been possible;

00:59:44.241 --> 00:59:46.950
but stilI you are under the grip of the elements,

00:59:47.450 --> 00:59:49.366
how can you control it ?

00:59:56.325 --> 01:00:01.159
First of all get out of the slavery, this mental slavery.

01:00:03.075 --> 01:00:07.575
"Alright if it is there, it is there, if it is not there it doesn't matter.

01:00:07.617 --> 01:00:09.450
Nothing is more important than me,

01:00:09.867 --> 01:00:11.575
I am the king of the whole world.

01:00:11.617 --> 01:00:13.742
If I have to sleep on the ground I can sleep,

01:00:13.742 --> 01:00:15.700
if I have to sleep in the palaces I can sleep,

01:00:15.700 --> 01:00:19.575
nothing can dominate me." Then you are the master.

01:00:21.533 --> 01:00:23.867
You know in India, there are some Sahaja Yogis

01:00:23.909 --> 01:00:29.450
who are controlling definitely controlling, elements.

01:00:29.992 --> 01:00:33.408
We have examples of that, lots of things have been published

01:00:33.450 --> 01:00:36.199
you know in Nirmala Yoga, you must have heard.

01:00:36.909 --> 01:00:39.200
But you meet them, you'll find they are avadhutas

01:00:39.241 --> 01:00:41.825
and when they talk you feel a great sage is talking,

01:00:41.867 --> 01:00:44.491
and the way they behave, all the time you see their behaviour

01:00:44.533 --> 01:00:46.117
and everything is so great.

01:00:46.159 --> 01:00:47.825
We need people of that calibre today,

01:00:47.867 --> 01:00:50.533
because that is the situation of all nations.

01:00:53.867 --> 01:00:58.159
You have to be extra-good, because today is not a time

01:00:58.199 --> 01:01:01.325
when we can allow things to go, as they are.

01:01:05.617 --> 01:01:08.159
Or we are not just disciples,

01:01:08.159 --> 01:01:10.034
we all have to become gurus.

01:01:13.075 --> 01:01:17.408
And it is not the time when you can play with time.

01:01:17.408 --> 01:01:23.491
You cannot play with evil. You have to surmount it.

01:01:23.533 --> 01:01:25.325
You have to come on top of it, it is the time

01:01:25.366 --> 01:01:28.075
when the whole ship is going to be drowned or saved.

01:01:28.117 --> 01:01:29.783
This is the situation today.

01:01:30.366 --> 01:01:33.491
And that's why you have got your realization from God.

01:01:34.200 --> 01:01:36.325
If that precarious time had not arrived,

01:01:36.366 --> 01:01:39.366
how many of you really think you deserved it?

01:01:40.075 --> 01:01:45.742
But you got it, because the time is such that everybody

01:01:45.742 --> 01:01:49.366
must be given realization, and they must be given all powers

01:01:49.408 --> 01:01:51.200
so that they come up.

01:01:51.241 --> 01:01:53.117
But if you do not open your heart,

01:01:53.159 --> 01:01:55.491
put all your attention to your Spirit,

01:01:55.491 --> 01:01:57.700
these powers will not work out.

01:01:57.742 --> 01:01:59.742
None of these powers will work out in you.

01:02:00.575 --> 01:02:02.867
This is the problem.

01:02:02.867 --> 01:02:05.992
Every Guru had a command on the elements.

01:02:06.533 --> 01:02:08.909
Nanaka, you know definitely.

01:02:09.366 --> 01:02:15.366
People were sitting there and they asked him for the water

01:02:15.825 --> 01:02:21.533
and he put his hand on a rock and the water started pouring down.

01:02:22.950 --> 01:02:26.199
That's why it is called Punjab, Punja :

01:02:26.867 --> 01:02:31.658
five; and the five rivers exist there, too.

01:02:35.617 --> 01:02:40.200
It is said about all of them that they had powers over the elements.

01:02:42.950 --> 01:02:45.159
So how much we are lacking ?

01:02:45.159 --> 01:02:50.575
Still we are like other people who are selling cheap things,

01:02:51.241 --> 01:02:59.575
or who are busy making cheap things, or who are of no value.

01:03:00.283 --> 01:03:02.825
You are the ones who have to save the whole world.

01:03:04.742 --> 01:03:08.575
And the maximum of my life, blood and toil and everything,

01:03:08.617 --> 01:03:10.950
sweat, I've put in this land of yours.

01:03:11.491 --> 01:03:13.617
And the time is coming for me to go.

01:03:14.117 --> 01:03:19.783
Only three years more are left; before that,

01:03:19.825 --> 01:03:22.199
I hope, we establish an ashram.

01:03:22.241 --> 01:03:23.825
We need not pay for it,

01:03:23.825 --> 01:03:28.075
but, you have to be ready to occupy it,

01:03:28.075 --> 01:03:30.117
otherwise you cannot occupy it I can tell you,

01:03:30.117 --> 01:03:32.450
you cannot get any more blessings of God.

01:03:33.241 --> 01:03:35.241
So why should God bless you ?

01:03:35.241 --> 01:03:37.117
This is the point one should ask oneself.

01:03:37.159 --> 01:03:42.700
Are you your own Spirit or you are all else but the Spirit!

01:03:44.867 --> 01:03:49.909
But when I say something, it just goes as a big roaring,

01:03:50.700 --> 01:03:54.034
I don't know if the frequency has reached your ears or not,

01:03:54.075 --> 01:03:56.950
but I would request you now,

01:03:56.992 --> 01:04:00.575
as Gavin has asked me for Guru Nanaka's day,

01:04:00.575 --> 01:04:02.199
I really didn't want to come.

01:04:02.199 --> 01:04:05.450
Because to talk of Guru Nanaka and to hear about him,

01:04:07.408 --> 01:04:10.199
one has to be a very great person.

01:04:14.366 --> 01:04:19.241
Because such a light to bear, you have to make up yourself.

01:04:19.283 --> 01:04:22.034
Everything else is important,

01:04:25.450 --> 01:04:30.366
then how can you talk of Sahaja Yoga coming there.

01:04:33.992 --> 01:04:36.034
I went to America, I was surprised!

01:04:36.034 --> 01:04:37.909
Americans whatever it is, few people,

01:04:37.909 --> 01:04:40.366
but to them Sahaja Yoga is the most important thing.

01:04:40.408 --> 01:04:43.034
They talk of nothing but Sahaja Yoga, their life is Sahaja Yoga,

01:04:43.075 --> 01:04:45.783
morning till evening they are working out Sahaja Yoga,

01:04:45.825 --> 01:04:48.783
nothing else, they are not bothered.

01:04:48.783 --> 01:04:50.617
Australians you know.

01:04:56.075 --> 01:05:04.241
But the Heart is not open, the Spirit has not shown its light.

01:05:04.909 --> 01:05:12.992
It is the one that gives you complete satisfaction, complete joy,

01:05:13.909 --> 01:05:18.075
complete Guru's principle, because then you start giving.

01:05:18.117 --> 01:05:20.491
If there is no light what are you giving? Darkness ?

01:05:22.783 --> 01:05:24.617
What are you giving to others ?

01:05:25.366 --> 01:05:29.408
The darkness that is within you, if you are going to give that....

01:05:32.783 --> 01:05:44.159
So the second phase, has to be, as I have told you, to have self respect.

